---
// About.astro
import SplitText from "../SplitText";
---

<section
  id="about"
  class="min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center items-center relative px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-12 xl:px-16 py-20 sm:py-24 md:py-32 bg-primary-2"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl w-full">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="mb-12 sm:mb-16 md:mb-20">
      <SplitText
        client:visible
        text="About Me"
        className="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl xl:text-8xl font-semibold"
        delay={100}
        duration={2}
        ease="elastic.out(1,0.3)"
        splitType="chars"
        from={{ opacity: 0, y: 40 }}
        to={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}
        threshold={0.1}
        rootMargin="-10px"
      />

      <!-- Decorative line -->
      <div class="w-20 sm:w-24 md:w-32 h-1 bg-gray-900 mt-6 sm:mt-8"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="space-y-6 sm:space-y-8 md:space-y-10">
      <p
        class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl leading-relaxed text-gray-800 font-light"
      >
        With fifteen years cultivating enterprise-grade software systems, I
        specialize in architecting scalable solutions that marry computational
        excellence with refined user experience.
      </p>

      <p
        class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl leading-relaxed text-gray-600 font-light"
      >
        My practice focuses on distributed systems, advanced algorithms, and
        performance optimizationâ€”bringing the precision of classical engineering
        principles to modern software architecture.
      </p>

      <p
        class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl leading-relaxed text-gray-600 font-light"
      >
        I collaborate exclusively with forward-thinking organizations that
        understand the value of thoughtful engineering and appreciate the
        distinction between merely functional code and truly elegant systems.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Skills/Expertise Section -->
    <div class="mt-16 sm:mt-20 md:mt-24">
      <h3
        class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-12 sm:mb-16"
      >
        Core Expertise
      </h3>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:gap-6">
        <div
          class="group relative bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-200 p-6 sm:p-8 hover:border-gray-900 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300"
        >
          <div
            class="absolute top-6 sm:top-8 right-6 sm:right-8 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-200 group-hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors duration-300"
          >
            01
          </div>
          <h4
            class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4 relative z-10"
          >
            System Architecture
          </h4>
          <p
            class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed relative z-10"
          >
            Designing scalable, maintainable distributed systems that stand the
            test of time and traffic
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="group relative bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-200 p-6 sm:p-8 hover:border-gray-900 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300"
        >
          <div
            class="absolute top-6 sm:top-8 right-6 sm:right-8 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-200 group-hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors duration-300"
          >
            02
          </div>
          <h4
            class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4 relative z-10"
          >
            Performance Optimization
          </h4>
          <p
            class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed relative z-10"
          >
            Fine-tuning systems for maximum efficiency through profiling,
            analysis, and strategic improvements
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="group relative bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-200 p-6 sm:p-8 hover:border-gray-900 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300"
        >
          <div
            class="absolute top-6 sm:top-8 right-6 sm:right-8 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-200 group-hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors duration-300"
          >
            03
          </div>
          <h4
            class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4 relative z-10"
          >
            User Experience
          </h4>
          <p
            class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed relative z-10"
          >
            Crafting intuitive interfaces that delight users while maintaining
            peak performance
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="group relative bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-200 p-6 sm:p-8 hover:border-gray-900 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300"
        >
          <div
            class="absolute top-6 sm:top-8 right-6 sm:right-8 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-200 group-hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors duration-300"
          >
            04
          </div>
          <h4
            class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4 relative z-10"
          >
            Advanced Algorithms
          </h4>
          <p
            class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed relative z-10"
          >
            Implementing efficient computational solutions backed by solid
            computer science fundamentals
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="group relative bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-200 p-6 sm:p-8 hover:border-gray-900 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300"
        >
          <div
            class="absolute top-6 sm:top-8 right-6 sm:right-8 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-200 group-hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors duration-300"
          >
            05
          </div>
          <h4
            class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4 relative z-10"
          >
            Code Quality
          </h4>
          <p
            class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed relative z-10"
          >
            Writing elegant, maintainable codebases with comprehensive testing
            and documentation
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="group relative bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-200 p-6 sm:p-8 hover:border-gray-900 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300"
        >
          <div
            class="absolute top-6 sm:top-8 right-6 sm:right-8 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-200 group-hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors duration-300"
          >
            06
          </div>
          <h4
            class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4 relative z-10"
          >
            Team Leadership
          </h4>
          <p
            class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed relative z-10"
          >
            Guiding teams toward technical excellence through mentorship and
            best practices
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Call to Action -->
    <div
      class="mt-16 sm:mt-20 md:mt-24 pt-12 sm:pt-16 border-t border-gray-300"
    >
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 mb-6 sm:mb-8">
        Interested in collaborating? Let's build something exceptional together.
      </p>
      <a
        href="#contact"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-900 font-medium text-lg hover:gap-4 transition-all duration-300 group"
      >
        <span>Get in touch</span>
        <svg
          class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
